\TBool$, and $t_2 \typeof \TBool$. We then do case analysis on $t
\stepsto t'$, where for each case $t' \typeof \TBool$, to prove the
theorem.

*  Case \infr{E-AndTrue}: $t_1 = \tTrue$ and $t' = t_2$. We know the
